  ✓ Share and recommend Noor UI to others

================================================================================

TRADEMARK RESTRICTIONS
================================================================================

To avoid confusion in the marketplace, please do NOT:
  ✗ Create a competing library or fork using the name "Noor UI"
  ✗ Publish packages to npm that include "Noor UI" in the name
  ✗ Use the Noor UI name or logo in ways that suggest official endorsement
  ✗ Remove copyright notices or attribution from the source code
  ✗ Misrepresent the origin or official source of the project

================================================================================

DERIVATIVE WORKS
================================================================================

If you create a derivative work or fork based on Noor UI:
  • Please give it a distinct, different name
  • Clearly state that it is derived from Noor UI
  • Maintain the original copyright notices in the code
  • Link back to the original project (appreciated but not required)

Example acceptable attribution:
"Based on Noor UI by Nuno Marques (https://github.com/ositaka/noor-ui)"

